    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>QMU Sport &amp; Fitness are delighted to be delivering Fitness Industry Qualification courses in collaboration with MBM Training (formally The EnergyWise Academy), in addition to our established First Aid courses.  MBM Training is renowned for its down to earth, realistic approach when applying the theory of qualifications to existing practical skills. We offer Level 2 Gym Instructor, Level 3 Personal Trainer and Indoor Cycling so why not come along and get your career started with us. </p>]]></Value>
